<html><head><meta charset='utf-8'><title>TOEIC Results</title></head><body><h1>TOEIC SPEAKING RESULTS</h1><h3>Part 7: IELTS Speaking (ID: P7-3.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all border-l-4 border-l-rose-500">
                        <img src="image/p7_img3_q1.png" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%2310b981' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%2310b981'%3EPart%207 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'">
