                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is the most famous vehicles in your country ?. Why ?.
one of the most famous vehicle in country is motorbike. 
-> convinient (go to anywhere at any time)
-> affordable (compare to the car, it is much cheaper).
-> motorbike is various in types and sizes.</p><hr><h3>Part 7: IELTS Speaking (ID: P7-3.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all border-l-4 border-l-rose-500">
                        <img src="image/p7_img3_q2.png" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%2310b981' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%2310b981'%3EPart%207 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'">
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-rose-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">IELTS Speaking Part 1 • Bicycle</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">How popular are bicycles in your country?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> How popular are bicycles in your country?
Bicyle is very famous in my country along with the motorbike. If the motorkbike is famous among the adult then the bicycle is really famous among the youth, because they are not eligable to certificates til they turn 18.  
-> Why ?.
Do you think the youth in Viet Nam use the bicycle to protect the environment ?.
For some people, they are aware of the environment problems so they use bicycle instead. This helps them to reduce emission, carbon footprint, .... This protect the envrionment. 
+) ----- (friendly).
N-concious: quan tâm về gì. 
health (environment)-concious kind of person: quan tâm 
</p><hr><h3>Part 7: IELTS Speaking (ID: P7-3.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all border-l-4 border-l-rose-500">
