                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is your favorite color? Why?

nature, people in my hometown. (__cảnh làng chài__). Everymorning, the fishmen often wake up early to go fishing, while the children build the sand castle, jump on the wave. Blue clean water and sky have been pictured in my mind. I can never forget that
     
</p><hr><h3>Part 7: IELTS Speaking (ID: P7-5.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all border-l-4 border-l-rose-500">
